  <title>Availability tactics</title>
  <para>
    Recall that a failure occurs only if a fault is allowed to develop into a user-detectable
    failure. Availability tactics focus on 
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem><para>
        detecting faults,
      </para></listitem>
      <listitem><para>
        preventing them from causing a failure,
      </para></listitem>
      <listitem><para>
        and recovering from the fault situation.   
      </para></listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </para>
  
